But there was supposed to be maintenance on the fields.

882
01:03:05,412 --> 01:03:06,512
So six years.

883
01:03:06,572 --> 01:03:08,413
Yes, it was supposed to be maintenance on the fields.

884
01:03:09,318 --> 01:03:12,400
Medford does a horrible job with maintenance in the general sense.

885
01:03:13,080 --> 01:03:16,623
Schools, streets, fields.

886
01:03:16,923 --> 01:03:17,743
We don't do a good job.

