895
01:03:46,499 --> 01:03:47,460
I took the fields over.

896
01:03:47,520 --> 01:03:48,080
I volunteered.

897
01:03:48,120 --> 01:03:48,641
I make a dime.

898
01:03:48,741 --> 01:03:49,581
I hired 10 people.

899
01:03:51,687 --> 01:03:55,751
a sweeping machine that just grooms the field.

900
01:03:56,191 --> 01:03:57,432
And that's supposed to do that weekly.

901
01:03:57,452 --> 01:03:58,313
And those guys do that.

902
01:03:58,833 --> 01:03:59,794
That's what they're told to do.

903
01:04:00,634 --> 01:04:05,638
Then, apparently, Joe Crowley comes up, and he sweeps the fields twice a year.

904
01:04:05,919 --> 01:04:06,619
He's just sweeping.

905
01:04:07,079 --> 01:04:08,280
It's not the deep cleaning.

906
01:04:08,340 --> 01:04:09,962
It's not the cleansing that needs to happen.

