01:16:46,811 --> 01:17:04,536
I applaud my colleagues, this is a very hot topic, this is a very important topic, and I think that's something we all recognize, and what I recognized six years ago on the school committee, is the lack of a maintenance plan that needs to be in place, and I think that we should be working on that.

1093
01:17:04,836 --> 01:17:13,359
But if we can recall back some odd years ago, and I think Mr. Carr can attest, the reason why we did these fields, and the reason why we could do these fields,

1094
01:17:14,380 --> 01:17:18,144
at the time it wasn't going to be funded by the taxpayer.

1095
01:17:18,505 --> 01:17:32,481
