1096
01:17:32,841 --> 01:17:33,963
And the only way to do that

1097
01:17:35,405 --> 01:17:42,912
The realistic way to do that is to strike a balance where there was rentals and giving our opportunity for our kids to play on those fields.

1098
01:17:43,413 --> 01:17:45,415
And that was the only way that there was the balance.

1099
01:17:46,215 --> 01:17:50,880
Unfortunately, to say that we would go and just build this and make it happen wasn't going to happen.

1100
01:17:51,340 --> 01:17:51,781
We know it.

1101
01:17:52,321 --> 01:17:52,802
We lived it.

1102
01:17:54,001 --> 01:17:56,083
