1103
01:17:56,483 --> 01:18:01,407
So we had to look at that, think outside the box, be creative, so our kids weren't playing on a dangerous field.

1104
01:18:01,427 --> 01:18:01,947
Because you know what?

1105
01:18:02,387 --> 01:18:05,830
Most of that time, those fields were closed because they were dangerous.

1106
01:18:06,190 --> 01:18:07,011
Let's not forget that.

1107
01:18:08,072 --> 01:18:18,479
To say that, you know, and not putting words in my colleague's mouth, but looking at books and looking at pens and pencils and paper,

1108
01:18:20,079 --> 01:18:21,020
To me, that's not fair.

1109
01:18:21,120 --> 01:18:27,005
For six years, I was on the school committee making sure that, trying to make sure we had checks and balances.

1110
01:18:27,725 --> 01:18:29,407
