1111
01:18:30,228 --> 01:18:34,451
Our classroom size is the best in the commonwealth, and our programs are thriving.

1112
01:18:35,312 --> 01:18:38,875
We have a beautiful science building, we have a beautiful pool, we have a beautiful place.

1113
01:18:38,915 --> 01:18:41,997
Now, don't get me wrong, there are definitely issues there.

1114
01:18:42,958 --> 01:18:43,759
Bubblers, you're right.

1115
01:18:44,039 --> 01:18:44,900
Bathrooms, you're right.

1116
01:18:46,381 --> 01:18:48,402
But I'd love to see a maintenance plan moving forward.

1117
01:18:48,862 --> 01:18:50,723
Counsel, you're correct, a thousand percent.

1118
01:18:51,423 --> 01:18:55,244
But to insinuate one rather than the other, it's not fair.

1119
01:18:55,945 --> 01:18:58,045
We needed these fields to work.

1120
01:18:58,446 --> 01:19:04,348
And the only way to make them work is find a balance from outside and what we have inside.

1121
01:19:05,388 --> 01:19:11,931
