1122
01:19:12,432 --> 01:19:16,554
But the realistic issues are, if we wanted them, this is what we needed to do.

1123
01:19:18,008 --> 01:19:27,694
And this wasn't George Scott Pelley's school committee member, this wasn't George Scott Pelley's city councilor, this was George Scott Pelley, a parent of a child that wanted to make sure that our kids played on safe fields.

1124
01:19:28,074 --> 01:19:31,216
That's what Billy Carr started back then, and this is what we went forward.

1125
01:19:31,636 --> 01:19:46,045
