01:25:37,178 --> 01:25:38,742
And it's going to be embarrassing.

1201
01:25:39,323 --> 01:25:41,048
So we don't want to get to that point.

1202
01:25:41,569 --> 01:25:44,717
Let's do the right thing and keep them going for the next five or six years, probably.

