01:25:48,445 --> 01:25:49,405
Good evening, citizen.

1204
01:25:49,505 --> 01:25:51,346
Please state your name and address for the record.

1205
01:25:51,586 --> 01:25:52,506
My name is Robert Penter.

1206
01:25:52,526 --> 01:25:54,346
I live at Zero Summit Road, Medford, Mass.

1207
01:25:54,547 --> 01:25:55,947
I'm a member of the Saugus party.

1208
01:25:56,607 --> 01:25:58,227
My take on this is just a little bit different.

1209
01:25:58,507 --> 01:26:01,568
We can talk about the maintenance, and it's quite obvious that the maintenance is an issue.

1210
01:26:02,128 --> 01:26:05,249
But I'd like to get into the legality of the bond in and of itself.

1211
01:26:05,809 --> 01:26:08,650
When the city of Medford went out for the bond in this particular field,

1212
01:26:11,715 --> 01:26:13,536
Point of information, Counselor Knight.

1213
01:26:13,656 --> 01:26:15,237
I'm going to get into the legality of matters.

1214
01:26:15,297 --> 01:26:19,861
I think I'd feel more comfortable if the city solicitor were present and able to provide us with that type of advice.

1215
01:26:20,481 --> 01:26:21,041
I would, too.

1216
01:26:21,282 --> 01:26:27,085
Mr. President, my purpose of saying the legality of it is because I would like to ask a question, and I think it needs to be answered.

1217
01:26:27,506 --> 01:26:28,566
The question is very simple.

1218
01:26:28,607 --> 01:26:29,927
The City of Meffitt owns the property.

1219
01:26:30,808 --> 01:26:34,811
Now, will the City of Meffitt own the dome that the renter wants to come in?

1220
01:26:35,511 --> 01:26:40,995
And if that's the situation, I think it changes the whole intent of what the City of Meffitt's bond was all about.

1221
01:26:41,533 --> 01:26:49,581
and that bond being for the exclusive use, again, of the fields, Medford folks and students first, and however the rentals take place.

1222
01:26:50,001 --> 01:26:59,170
But you're now building a bond, and now you want to build a bubble, and the bubble will declare an ownership of authority of the person that has it, and the city of Medford will not have priority of the use of those fields.

1223
01:26:59,791 --> 01:27:05,737
So I would hope one of you folks on the council would make that request to our city solicitor to ask him

1224
01:27:06,180 --> 01:27:17,024
if in fact this is even legal to do and what authority, if anything, does the city or will they have over the dome itself for the purposes of liability and for the purposes of its use?

1225
01:27:17,444 --> 01:27:19,184
I think it's an important question to ask.

1226
01:27:20,025 --> 01:27:22,646
I have no problem with the bubble, whether it goes or doesn't go.

1227
01:27:22,906 --> 01:27:25,747
I think you need to have this legal question as it relates to this particular matter.

1228
01:27:26,767 --> 01:27:27,127
Thank you.

1229
01:27:27,827 --> 01:27:28,968
So I would hope somebody.

1230
01:27:28,988 --> 01:27:33,889
I can move that question, Mr. President.

1231
01:27:33,909 --> 01:27:35,790
Please state the question, Councilor Marks.

1232
01:27:36,650 --> 01:27:39,091
The question is the liability of the bubble.

1233
01:27:39,131 --> 01:27:43,453
Who would be responsible for the maintenance and upkeep of the bubble?

1234
01:27:44,553 --> 01:27:48,415
In case of some type of disaster, what would happen?

1235
01:27:48,455 --> 01:27:50,136
Would the City of Meffitt be responsible?

1236
01:27:50,756 --> 01:27:52,057
Who maintains ownership?

1237
01:27:53,077 --> 01:27:56,118
On the motion of Councilor Night, there is an additional, sir.

1238
01:27:56,518 --> 01:27:56,939
Also one.

1239
01:27:57,639 --> 01:27:57,839
Sir.

1240
01:27:57,859 --> 01:27:59,079
