1243
01:28:05,706 --> 01:28:08,228
I'm trying to clarify the motion, if you'd give me the courtesy.

1244
01:28:10,109 --> 01:28:23,537
Also, the fact of the matter is, does this interfere with the bond that originally was written, therefore allowing, as such right now, the city of Method entertaining a private entity to come in, use its field for its particular purpose, the dome?

1245
01:28:23,958 --> 01:28:25,419
I think that question needs to be asked.

1246
01:28:26,639 --> 01:28:27,640
Thank you.

1247
01:28:27,820 --> 01:28:29,862
So moved, Mr. President, that that be asked.

