1251
01:28:40,991 --> 01:28:42,412
My name is Carolyn Jones.

1252
01:28:42,512 --> 01:28:44,353
I live at 32 Arlington Street.

1253
01:28:46,174 --> 01:28:59,100
I was sitting back listening to the conversation particularly about this dome and the field versus the educational side of public schools in Medford.

1254
01:28:59,140 --> 01:29:07,264
And I think that the conversation sort of got askew because it's really very necessary

1255
01:29:07,995 --> 01:29:18,742
for the students to have a place where they can be active, since I don't think that they really have that many gym courses that get them out to be active.

1256
01:29:18,982 --> 01:29:22,844
But I think more important than that is the education that they get.

1257
01:29:23,585 --> 01:29:26,627
I taught at Medford High School eons ago.

1258
01:29:28,208 --> 01:29:29,488
I only taught for one year.

1259
01:29:30,309 --> 01:29:33,351
The reason why I only taught for one year is that I'm a shoe freak.

1260
01:29:34,253 --> 01:29:45,716
And I had all of these shoes, and standing on my feet, my shoes, my feet grew like a size larger, and I said, I can't do this every year if I have to buy new shoes.

1261
01:29:46,817 --> 01:29:50,898
And so I decided to move on, and I went into the private sector.

1262
01:29:51,518 --> 01:30:01,181
But one of the things that disturbed me when I taught was that the, I taught history and civics, and the books were antiquated.

1263
01:30:02,356 --> 01:30:08,262
And so I had some relatives who were educators, and they didn't live in Massachusetts.

1264
01:30:08,783 --> 01:30:16,591
And I said, what books can you send me that I can use to teach civics and history in a way that I want the students to understand it?

1265
01:30:17,933 --> 01:30:19,434
And they sent me some books.

1266
01:30:19,594 --> 01:30:24,820
Now, they sent me books for me to use, so that meant that I had to spend more time developing

1267
01:30:26,568 --> 01:30:28,789
the script for the courses that I taught.

1268
01:30:31,010 --> 01:30:37,092
And my classroom was next door to the senior submaster's office.

1269
01:30:38,112 --> 01:30:46,255
And I was told that that was where they put first year teachers because he thought that they could not control themselves or the class.

1270
01:30:47,156 --> 01:30:51,057
And about halfway through the year, he came and he stood in the back of my class

1271
01:30:51,951 --> 01:30:55,653
At the end of the class, I said, is there something I can help you with?

1272
01:30:55,733 --> 01:30:58,675
And he said, I never hear any noise coming from your class.

1273
01:30:59,495 --> 01:31:02,217
And I said, that's because you're not supposed to hear any noise.

1274
01:31:03,277 --> 01:31:14,704
And I developed my own curriculum for what I taught the students that I thought would keep them interested in history and civics, because I know that that's not

1275
01:31:15,647 --> 01:31:18,008
those are not classes that most students liked.

1276
01:31:18,408 --> 01:31:22,330
Unfortunately, when I was in high school, those were my favorite classes.

1277
01:31:23,691 --> 01:31:42,599
I think that Medford High School, all of Medford schools, need to keep up in terms of the books that you use, the curriculum that you help the teachers design, whether they do it on their own, whether they do it collectively.

